auth_verification_steps.description: Steps to verify authentication and authorization mechanisms.

vulnerability_scan_strategy.description: Tools and frequency for security scanning (e.g. OWASP ZAP).

summary.description: A technical, 1-sentence summary of the QA strategy.

description.description: Detailed verification philosophy and test plan.

test_strategy.unit: Jest for NestJS services/controllers and React Native components. Strict mocking of repositories.
test_strategy.integration: Supertest for API endpoints using Dockerized Test DB. Verify ACID transactions and constraints.
test_strategy.e2e: Detox for critical mobile flows (Login, Transfer). Mocking biometric hardware responses.
test_strategy.approach: Test Pyramid strategy emphasizing heavy backend logic coverage and automated security gates.

test_cases.name: Biometric Login Verification
test_cases.description: Verify server-side validation of cryptographic signature from device biometrics.
test_cases.expected_result: Access token issued only on valid signature.
test_cases.gherkin: GIVEN a registered user with FaceID WHEN they sign the nonce with private key THEN the server validates public key AND issues JWT.

test_cases.name: Internal Transfer ACID Compliance
test_cases.description: Ensure atomic debit and credit operations during funds transfer.
test_cases.expected_result: Total system balance remains constant; no partial updates.
test_cases.gherkin: GIVEN Account A has 100 AND Account B has 0 WHEN transferring 50 from A to B THEN A is 50 AND B is 50 AND transaction record exists.

test_cases.name: Dashboard Balance Decryption
test_cases.description: Verify encrypted balance in DB is correctly decrypted for display.
test_cases.expected_result: User sees correct numeric balance, not cipher text.
test_cases.gherkin: GIVEN an authenticated user WHEN the dashboard loads THEN the balance API returns decrypted values AND UI formats currency.

test_cases.name: High Value Transaction Alert
test_cases.description: Verify push notification trigger on large debit.
test_cases.expected_result: FCM message sent to user device.
test_cases.gherkin: GIVEN a notification threshold of $500 WHEN a debit of $600 occurs THEN a push notification event is queued in Redis.

auth_verification_steps: Verify JWT signature and expiration enforcement.
Validate cryptographic nonce uniqueness to prevent replay attacks.
Check rate limiting on login endpoints (5 attempts/min).
security_plan.vulnerability_scan_strategy: Weekly OWASP ZAP scans on API endpoints; Snyk scans on CI/CD for dependency vulnerabilities.

manual_verification_steps: Verify physical biometric prompt appears on iOS and Android devices.
Test UI responsiveness when device is in Airplane mode (graceful degradation).
Visual inspection of currency formatting across different locales.
Verify deep linking from push notifications opens correct transaction detail.

risk_analysis.mitigation: Enforce server-side signature verification; do not rely on client-side boolean.
Use database-level transaction isolation (SERIALIZABLE) and row locking.
Implement log masking for sensitive fields (password, balance, account numbers).

content.summary: A security-first QA strategy leveraging automated testing for financial integrity and manual validation for biometric hardware integration.
content.description: The plan prioritizes backend data integrity through rigorous integration testing of ACID transactions. Mobile testing focuses on the 'Happy Path' via Detox, while security testing is integrated into the CI pipeline to ensure compliance with banking regulations and encryption standards.
